This code integrates AR functionality using the `ar.js` library, which allows for the display of real-time data on crop growth and health. The `arOptions` variable contains the configuration for the AR pattern marker, and the `/ar` endpoint generates an AR image with the real-time data. The AR functionality can be further integrated with real-time data from IoT sensors and ML algorithms.
